title: Best of The Program | Guest: Janice Dean | 2/1/21
description:
Pat Gray joins to talk how silver is the next GameStop and how vastly different equity is from equality. Fox News senior meteorologist Janice Dean breaks down the latest in Andrew Cuomo’s nursing home scandal. Are we witnessing a prelude to the brave new world? Glenn explains how fast America is becoming an oligarchy.
